title: Tranquil Lifestyle 🌳✨ Jr. One Bedroom with Patio, W/D & More! 🏡
neighborhood: Long Beach, CSULB, Bixby Village, Belmont Shores, Naples
posting_body: ['Pathways @ Bixby Village', '5980 Bixby Village Dr.', 'Long Beach, CA 90803', 'show contact info', 'If you love a quiet, lush outdoor space with beautiful landscape and area to enjoy the outdoors, look no further!', 'You will find everything you need plus more at Pathways!', 'We are located in the beautiful area of Bixby Village surrounded with abundant greenery and tranquil lifestyle!', 'We currently have a one bedroom apartment available for move-in on September 5!', 'Our Naples floor plan has 528 sq.ft.', 'of living space plus a private outdoor space for you to enjoy!', 'Apartment', '#79008', 'is located on the frst floor and features an outdoor patio!', 'Our apartments are fully renovated and feature gleaming stainless steel appliances including a refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, and microwave!', 'Washer and dryers are also included!', "Don't miss out on this beautiful home!", 'Call us today to schedule a self-guided tour!', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit https://essexapts.info/Pathways-at-Bixby-Village to schedule a tour online.', 'Community Amenities', '**Fully equipped fitness center', '**Heated pool and hot tub', '**Dog park & pet spa', '**Clubhouse with WIFI and Billiards', '**Several community BBQ grilling areas', '**Outdoor lounge areas with games', '**Relaxing location', '**Park-like setting', '**Walking trails nearby', '**Walking distance to Target, CSULB and VA hospital', '**Close and easy access to 22, 605 and 405 Freeways', '**Close to Marina/ Mothers Beach', 'THE ESSEX DIFFERENCE:', '30-Day Satisfaction Guarantee', 'We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee with any leased apartment.', 'If you’re not 100% satisfied with your new home, we’ll help you transfer to a comparable home within the same community or you can choose to terminate your lease.*', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability subject to change']
